channel.title: Rs2-Devolution V3 Server Release (*508*)
channel.description:
[size=20pt][b]Rs2-Devolution 508 V3[/b][/size]
[b]Before you go on please read. Honestly, I can see why most people don't release their work, maybe because they spent hours doing it and feel that people don't deserve that way. Yesterday from 6 pm to 11 pm I was working on this server non-stop. I dedicated myself to finish it off, and then I suddenly felt overwhelmed and said to myself "Why should I give this to anyone" But then I shook out of my retarded state of being, and went back to work. But I realized how easy it is to be greedy. Just thought I could share that with everybody. [/b]
Features: Godwars:
[*]Bandos- General Graardor [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/bandoss.jpg[/img] [*]Zamorak- K'ril Tsutsaroth [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/zamorakk.jpg[/img] [*]Armadyl- Kree'Arra [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/armadyll.jpg[/img] [*]Saradomin- Commander Zilyana [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/saradominn.jpg[/img] [/list] ~King Black Dragon [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/kbdd.jpg[/img] ~Tz-Tok Jad [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/jadd.jpg[/img] ~NEW TRAINING AREA here is a picture. [IMG]http://[IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/newtrainingarea.jpg[/img][/IMG] ~Decent PKing ~Bounty Hunter (just the basic Bounty everyone has: no skulls or targets ) [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/bhh.jpg[/img] ~Kalphite Queen with minions all around here. Two forms, but they are standing side-by-side. [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/kqq.jpg[/img] ~Very newby friendly, has ::help and ::commands to guide you through the ENTIRE server.
[b]Server download link:[/b] [url=http://uppit.com/EQ3CDI]http://uppit.com/EQ3CDI[/url][/SIZE][/U]
Client suggestions: I recommend using Graham's Ipchanger
Future Updates for v2:
[*]Make Kalphite queen turn into her second form when she dies. [*]Make King Black Dragon use dragon fire, and require anti dragon fire shield. [*]More to come... [/list]
Here is a virus scan for the people who actually think there are viruses in JAVA format. (uh huh...) [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn129/Scyrnn/scanfornoobs.jpg[/img]
Credits:
Palidino76 Jagex Rs2-Devolution And the community for the motivation
EDIT::I am pretty new at Java so give me a break.
[u][b]I do not host any servers, so if you see one with the owner name Solstice, it is NOT me.[/b][/u]
[B]Please post and comment.[/B] [b]
Other Account Link Is On Rune Server[/b]
